staxel.village.character.dialogue.FarmFa: (안함)Do you think we could get a tractor around here?
(안함)I've always wanted to drive a real tractor...
(안함)There's so much I love about farming, I'm not sure where to start...
(안함)There are so many tasks to do but I can't figure out what to do first!
(안함)Wow! I still can't believe I'm actually living on a farm!
(안함)A farm I'm actually allowed to live on!
